HEADWORD: Congestive
<hw>Con*gest"ive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, indicating, or attended with, congestion in some
part of the body; <as>as, a <ex>congestive</ex> fever</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
